             was indicted for <rs id="t17960914-90-off500" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17960914-90-off500" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960914-90-off500" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17960914-90-cd501" type="crimeDate">16th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960914-90-off500 t17960914-90-cd501"></join>, a linen shirt, value 2s. 6d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17960914-90-victim882" type="victimName">
                     Joseph 
                     Neale
                  <interp inst="t17960914-90-victim882" type="surname" value="Neale"></interp>
