                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960914-90-defend880 t17960914-90-punish505"></join>
               Confined twelve months in the House of Correction
            </rs>, <rs id="t17960914-90-punish506" type="punishmentDescription">
